  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. This model has been applied in clinical research to support regulatory submissions for Class II spinal fixation devices. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Package conforms to the Minimal profile; structured context-of-use binding is deferred to a subsequent full-profile submission.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/f1717-compression-bending-static-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/fea-predicts-f1717-structural-performance",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-experimental-n11-lab1",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-experimental-n11-lab2"
  ],
